Package: libghostty-vt0-tip
Version: GHOSTTY_VERSION-BUILD_VERSION~DIST
Architecture: amd64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libc6
Description: Ghostty terminal VT core library (shared runtime, nightly)
 Weekly build of the libghostty-vt shared library from the upstream
 main branch. Provides the terminal VT engine used by Ghostty, for
 use by third-party applications. Tracks development code and may be
 unstable.
 .
 Install the stable `libghostty-vt0` package if you want a release
 build.
